1 install cmake-2.6.0, thrift-0.9.0, log4cplus-1.1.1, gtest-1.3.0
2 install libvirt kvm lxc
3 build:
    cd $LYNN_HOME
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..      # twice
    make
    make install  # install scheduler collector executor into bin/

To compile common lib, you need to do the following:
yum instal glibc-devel.i686
